title: What's your vision for the next 3 months?
message:
From SOUL.md and USER.md, I know passive income through vibe coding is a core goal. Right now I see you juggling maintenance (CoinUsUp, Even Us Up) + growth (Signal App) + OpenClaw infrastructure + consulting.

Where should I focus energy to best support your goals? Is it:
- Growing revenue on an existing app?
- Shipping the Signal App faster?
- Building new passive income vehicles?
- Reducing toil on OpenClaw maintenance?
- Something else entirely?
userAnswer: I think all those goals are good items to tackle, plan an implementation strategy for those items.
